                    <img src="assets/images/how-it-works/anchoring.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="features-img">
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">

                <div class="feature-detail">
                    <h1 class="title animated fadeInRight wow">Bitcoin Blockchain anchoring</h1>
                    <p class="features-txt animated fadeInRight wow">Anchoring is the process of periodically saving to a public source a fingerprint of system state. This approach negates the need for users to trust the system operator. Exonum is unique in using its' approach which enhances the security of already cryptographically proven systems and creates perfectly trustless environment.</p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
